\begin_layout Standard
Variations in the gain clearly do not arise from a static output nonlinearity,
 such as one associated with a static linear-nonlinear transformation 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "Dayan:2001uy"

\end_inset

